=== Federated Reinforcement Learning for Robotics

    \n
- My research project “Federated Learning for Multi-Robotics Cooperation” got funded with 500,000rmb from AIRS! (Apr. 2021-Mar. 2022). 
\n I lead this project with two excellent research interns Wenli Xiao and Tingwei Ye from CUHK(SZ). Check out our developed demo and cool NAO robots on the left side.

- I participated in the WeBank-AIRS collaboration project “Federated Reinforcement Learning”, led by Prof. Qiang Yang and Prof. Jianwei Huang. (Nov. 2020-Oct. 2022)
