=== Optimization and System Development for Federated Learning in Mobile and IoT Networks

    \n
- This is a collaborative research project with Prof. Jianwei Huang, Prof. Leandros Tassiulas, Dr. Shiqiang Wang, and research intern Xiang Li. Our goal is to design an efficient and effective federated learning system via optimizing key control parameters. Check our Heterogeneous Federated learning prototype on the left side.  

- Our paper “Cost-Effective Federated Learning Design” got accepted in IEEE International Conference on Computer Communications (INFOCOM), 2021. 
